 \int_{\partial M}\omega = \sum_i\int_{\partial M}\phi_i\omega = \sum_i\int_Md(\phi_i\omega) = \sum_i\int_{U_i}d(\alpha_i^*(\phi_i\omega)) = \sum_i\int_{U_i}d((\phi_i \circ \alpha_i)(\alpha_i^*\omega)) 
